<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Your Learning Experience Awaits</title>
</head>
<style>
  * {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      body {
        background-color: #f9fafb;
      }

      main {
        box-shadow: 0px 1px 3px 0px #0000000d;
      }

      .container {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
      }
    }
  }
</style>

<body>
  <div class="container" style="display: grid; height: 100vh">
    <main style="
          max-width: 528px;
          width: Fixed (528px) px;
          height: Hug (806px) px;
          padding: 40px 24px 24px 24px;
          gap: 40px;
          border-radius: 8px 0px 0px 0px;
          opacity: 0px;
          background-color: #fff;
        ">
      <img style="height: 40px; object-fit: contain; margin-bottom: 40px" src="{{{logoUrl}}}" />

      <div>
        <h1 style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 40px">
          Your Learning Experience Awaits
        </h1>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 40px">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
            Dear {{recipient}},
          </p>

          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
            Welcome to Nudgyt! Dive into engaging simulations and interactive
            scenarios designed to help you enhance your skills and reach your
            goals.
          </p>

          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
            Enjoy 2 weeks of unlimited access to all our services, free of
            charge. After your free trial, you’ll have the option to subscribe
            and continue unlocking your full potential.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a href="{{{url}}}">
          <button style="
              text-decoration: none;
              background-color: #5c05f2;
              padding: 12px 32px 12px 32px;
              border-radius: 4px;
              color: #fff;
              border: none;
              cursor: pointer;
            " onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.9'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">
            Start Learning
          </button>
        </a>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 40px; margin-top: 40px">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
            If you have any questions or need support, feel free to reach out to
            us at {{supportEmail}}.
          </p>

          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
            Welcome aboard!
          </p>

          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              font-weight: 500;
              line-height: 24.8px;
              text-align: left;
              text-underline-position: from-font;
              color: #727679;
              text-decoration-skip-ink: none;
            ">
            Best regards,<br />
            The Nudgyt Team
          </p>
        </div>
        <hr style="margin-bottom: 40px" />
        <div>
          <img src="{{{logoUrl}}}" style="height: 20px; object-fit: contain" />
          <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #727679">
            © 2025 Nudgyt Pte. Ltd. <br />
            Singapore
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>

</html>